{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1673-06_035","@resp":"mercure","head":{"value":"[Dialogue d’un Berger &amp; d’une Bergere, mise en musique par M. Vignon]","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Le Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", 1673 (tome VI), p. 35-37.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"Cette Chanson me fait ressouvenir d’un Dialogue que vous serez peut-estre bien aise d’apprendre, quoy qu’il ne soit pas sur la prise de Mastric : Il a esté mis en Musique par un grand Maistre, &amp; vous n’en douterez pas, quand vous sçaurez que c’est Monsieur Vignon.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"@rend":"border","#":[{"label":[{"@rend":"center b","#":{"value":"Dialogue d’un","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"center b","#":{"value":"Berger &amp; d’une Bergere.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label[1]/#"}}]},{"speaker":{"value":"Le Berger.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/speaker"}},{"l":["ENfin apres une cruelle absence,","Je revois les beaux yeux qui sçurent m’engager."]},{"speaker":{"value":"La Bergere.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/speaker"}},{"l":["Enfin apres une si longue absence,","Je retrouve en ces lieux mon fidele Berger."]},{"speaker":{"value":"Le Berger.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/speaker"}},{"l":{"value":"O l’heureux jour !","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/l"}},{"speaker":{"value":"La Bergere.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/speaker"}},{"l":{"space":[{},{}],"#":{"value":"O le bonheur extreme !","id":"/div/quote/#[8]/l/#"}}},{"speaker":{"value":"Le Berger.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/speaker"}},{"l":{"value":"Ah qu’il est doux de revoir ce qu’on aime !","id":"/div/quote/#[10]/l"}},{"speaker":{"value":"La Bergere.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/speaker"}},{"l":{"value":"Tirsis !","id":"/div/quote/#[12]/l"}},{"speaker":{"value":"Le Berger.","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/speaker"}},{"l":{"space":{},"#":{"value":"Philis !","id":"/div/quote/#[14]/l/#"}}},{"speaker":{"value":"La Bergere.","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/speaker"}},{"l":{"space":[{},{}],"#":{"value":"Beaux yeux !","id":"/div/quote/#[16]/l/#"}}},{"speaker":{"value":"Le Berger.","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/speaker"}},{"l":{"space":{},"#":{"value":"Adorables attraits !","id":"/div/quote/#[18]/l/#"}}},{"speaker":{"value":"Ensemble.","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/speaker"}},{"l":{"value":"Puisqu’un sort si doux nous rassemble.","id":"/div/quote/#[20]/l"}},{"speaker":{"value":"La Bergere.","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/speaker"}},{"l":{"value":"Ne nous separons point.","id":"/div/quote/#[22]/l"}},{"speaker":{"value":"Le Berger.","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/speaker"}},{"l":{"space":[{},{}],"#":{"value":"Ne nous quittons jamais","id":"/div/quote/#[24]/l/#"}}},{"speaker":{"value":"Ensemble","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/speaker"}},{"l":{"value":"Et vivons &amp; mourons ensemble.","id":"/div/quote/#[26]/l"}}]}}}